node.text: I'm so happy to share that our family’s favorite @crocs are working toward being Net Zero by 2030! Today they are starting production on the shoe of the future powered by a bio-based sustainable ingredient while still providing the same look, feel and function we all know and love. Cheers to comfort without carbon 🌍🤍#comfortwithoutcarbon #AD

my newest obsession 🤍💄
@beautycounter just launched a new all in one water resistant mascara with an amazing clean formula! It is made with a tripeptide ingredient that helps your lashes grow and it’s soft flexible brush gives your eyelashes lift, length, and volume without mineral oil and cyclic silicones! 
Check out my story to see how this mascara transforms ♡ 

#cleanbeauty #thinkbiggerthinkbetter #betterbeauty #beautycounterpartner
